<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>About Roadie</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      font-family: sans-serif;
    }

    .frame-layer {
      position: absolute;
      top: 80px;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .shape {
      position: absolute;
      opacity: 0.9;
      transform: rotate(var(--rotate, 0deg));
      clip-path: polygon(var(--clip));
    }

    .shape1 {
      background-color: #96320E;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 180px;
      height: 100%;
      --clip: 0 0, 70% 0, 100% 100%, 0 100%;
    }

    .shape2 {
      background-color: #EB6937;
      top: 0;
      right: 0;
      width: 260px;
      height: 100%;
      --clip: 20% 0, 100% 30%, 100% 100%, 0% 90%;
      --rotate: -2deg;
    }

    .shape3 {
      background-color: #F18A60;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 180px;
      width: calc(100% - 440px);
      height: 40px;
      --clip: 0 10%, 100% 0%, 100% 100%, 0% 100%;
      --rotate: 0deg;
    }

    .shape4 {
      background-color: #FAD6C7;
      top: 20px;
      left: 160px;
      width: calc(100% - 180px);
      height: 60px;
      --clip: 0 0, 100% 0, 85% 100%, 0% 80%;
      --rotate: 0deg;
    }

    .content-container {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      padding: 100px 60px 160px 60px;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    .top-right-img {
      float: right;
      width: 280px;
      margin-left: 40px;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .bottom-left-img {
      float: left;
      width: 220px;
      margin-right: 40px;
      margin-top: 60px;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .vertical-title {
      writing-mode: vertical-rl;
      transform: rotate(180deg);
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color:rgb(255, 255, 255);
      position: absolute;
      left: 40px;
      top: 160px;
    }

    .main-text {
      margin-top: 40px;
      margin-left: 160px;
      max-width: 600px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="frame-layer">
    <div class="shape shape1"></div>
    <div class="shape shape2"></div>
    <div class="shape shape3"></div>
    <div class="shape shape4"></div>
  </div>


  <div class="content-container">
<%= link_to root_path do %>
    <%= image_tag "back-button.png", alt: "Back button", class: "back-button" %>
    <% end %>
    <div class="vertical-title">About Us</div>
    <div class="d-flex">
      <div class="main-text">
        <h2>Why We Started Roadie</h2>
        <p>Music is built on connection — between rhythms, voices, instruments, and above all, people. Yet finding the right collaborators can often feel harder than writing the perfect hook. That is why we created Roadie — a platform designed to help musicians, vocalists, producers, and bands discover each other with ease and purpose.
            Behind the scenes, we are a trio of music lovers and tech entrepreneurs — James, Milo, and Admir — who built this platform under the guidance and mentorship of Le Wagon London. Our mission is simple: to empower creatives to connect, collaborate, and make music happen.
          Whether you're in your bedroom studio or selling out gigs, there's a space for you here.
        </p>
      </div>
      <%= image_tag "the_roadie_boys.png" , class: "roadie-float" %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
